At one point, the view from the on-board camera is obscured as water sprays up over the deck.

Dramatic video of the crossing, posted on the US Navy Facebook page, has already been viewed by nearly 1.5million people and shared more than 17,000 times.

Facebook user Doug Fryczynski wrote: 'Getting seasick just watching.'

